## White Listing TLDs
## http://www.seobythesea.com/2006/01/googles-most-popular-and-least-popular-top-level-domains/
## Reject TLDs that dont match
\.+(?!(com|net|org|us|edu|mil|gov|biz))$

## Blocking Comment Sites
\.+(spot.im|disqus.com|livefyre.com)$

## Block Facebook, Twitter
#\.+(facebook.com|fbcdn.net|fb.me|fbsbx.com)$
#\.+(twitter.com|twimg.com)$

## Testing Section
^metrics?[-.]

## Mmotti's List| Ref: https://github.com/mmotti/pihole-regex
^(.+[-_.])??[m]?ad[sxv]?[0-9]*[-_.]
^adim(age|g)s?[0-9]*[-_.]
^adse?rv(e(rs?)?|ices?)?[0-9]*[-.]
^adtrack(er|ing)?[0-9]*[-.]
^advert(s|is(ing|ements?))?[0-9]*[-_.]
^aff(iliat(es?|ion))?[-.]
^analytics?[-.]
^banners?[-.]
^beacons?[0-9]*[-.]
^count(ers?)?[0-9]*[-.]
^pixels?[-.]
^stat(s|istics)?[0-9]*[-.]o
^telemetry[-.]
^track(ers?|ing)?[0-9]*[-.]
^traff(ic)?[-.]
